001
002package com.commercetools.api.predicates.query;
003
004public interface InequalityPredicateBuilder<T, TValue> extends ComparablePredicateBuilder<T, TValue> {
005    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isLessThan(final TValue value) {
006        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_LESS_THAN, value);
007    }
008
009    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isGreaterThan(final TValue value) {
010        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_GREATER_THAN, value);
011    }
012
013    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isLessThanOrEqual(final TValue value) {
014        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_LESS_THAN_OR_EQUAL, value);
015    }
016
017    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isGreaterThanOrEqual(final TValue value) {
018        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUAL, value);
019    }
020
021    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isLessThanVar(final String variable) {
022        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_LESS_THAN, VariableQueryPredicate.of().constant(variable));
023    }
024
025    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isGreaterThanVar(final String variable) {
026        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_GREATER_THAN, VariableQueryPredicate.of().constant(variable));
027    }
028
029    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isLessThanOrEqualVar(final String variable) {
030        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_LESS_THAN_OR_EQUAL, VariableQueryPredicate.of().constant(variable));
031    }
032
033    default CombinationQueryPredicate<T> isGreaterThanOrEqualVar(final String variable) {
034        return is(PredicateOperator.IS_GREATER_THAN_OR_EQUAL, VariableQueryPredicate.of().constant(variable));
035    }
036}
